title: How To Install a K&N Air Intake on a 2015-2016 Chevy Colorado/GMC Canyon 3.6L
description:
See how easy it is to install a K&N air intake on your 2015-2016 Chevy Colorado or GMC Canyon 3.6L.

K&N 63-3088 performance air intake system is easy to install and guaranteed to increase horsepower in 2015-2016 Chevy Colorado or GMC Canyon with a 3.6L engine. When dyno tested, this air intake created an estimated gain of 19.41hp horsepower at 3551 RPM.

This air intake includes an oversized washable & reusable air filter that can go up to 100,000 miles between servicing. K&N air intake 63-3088 also includes a free flowing polyethylene rotomolded intake tube and aluminum heat shield to isolate intake air from engine heat.
